  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Jesús Salvawajniyta rikuyta munashani;
 Payqa tíyasqa kashan janaj pacha gloriampi./
 
[C]
 /Kutimuynín qayllaña, manachu suyashankí?
 Jesusta qhesachaspa, waqayman qan ríshanki./
 
[V2]
 /Pay glorianta saqespa, kay pachamanjamorqa,
 Munakuyta rikuchin kay laqhayaj mundoman./
 
[V3]
 /Calvario k'aspi cruzpi Diospa Churin wañorqa,
 Chay cruzpi wañusqanwan Payqa rantiwarqanchej.
 
</lyrics></song>